[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/blackwood"]
[Student "S"]
{When WEST opens 1NT EAST hopes his hand includes all four Aces so she can bid 7NT. 
So she uses Gerber to find out.

But, when she discovers they are missing an Ace she settles for 6NT.}

